      <h1>西安房价会走向合理区间 房企将上演&quot;大鱼吃小鱼&quot;</h1>
      <h2>时间:<span id="pubtime_baidu">2014-10-26 07:28:15</span>来源:<span id="source_baidu">华商报</span><span>作者:<span id="author_baidu">黄涛</span></span>编辑:<span id="editor_baidu">顾柠语</span></h2>
